{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030", "id": 326101820, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzMjYxMDE4MjA=", "number": 51030, "title": "`make_`, `to_`, and `into_` methods for in-place, cloning, and \"eating\" conversions, respectively", "user": {"login": "SoniEx2", "id": 1779619, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3Nzk2MTk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1779619?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2", "html_url": "https://github.com/SoniEx2", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2018-05-24T12:36:54Z", "updated_at": "2018-05-24T12:41:12Z", "closed_at": "2018-05-24T12:41:11Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "I would like the stdlib to follow the following rules for conversion methods:\r\n\r\n- `make_`\r\n    - Converts in-place.\r\n    - Returns `()` or `Result<(), E>`.\r\n- `to_`\r\n    - Creates a new object for the conversion.\r\n    - Returns `T` or `Result<T, E>`.\r\n- `into_`\r\n    - May or may not actually create a new object. Consumes the current object (i.e. takes an `self`/`mut self`).\r\n    - Returns `T` or `Result<T, E>`.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nlet hello = String::from(\"Hello World\");\r\nlet hello_new = hello.to_ascii_lowercase();\r\nassert_eq!(hello_new, \"hello world\");\r\nassert_eq!(hello, \"Hello World\");\r\n\r\nlet mut hello = String::from(\"Hello World\");\r\nhello.make_ascii_lowercase();\r\nassert_eq!(hello, \"hello world\");\r\n\r\nlet hello = String::from(\"Hello World\");\r\nlet hello_moved = hello.into_ascii_lowercase();\r\nassert_eq!(hello_moved, \"hello world\");\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe main benefits of the `into_` methods is that the compiler knows how to optimize them, as they don't necessarily hit the allocator (certainly not in the `into_ascii_lowercase` case), which can be nice for [some things](https://internals.rust-lang.org/t/string-into-ascii-lowercase/7582).", "closed_by": {"login": "SoniEx2", "id": 1779619, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3Nzk2MTk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1779619?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2", "html_url": "https://github.com/SoniEx2", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/SoniEx2/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/51030/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}